    <title>辛苦大佬帮我看看</title>
    <url>/2023/03/29/%E6%90%AD%E5%BB%BA%E8%87%AA%E5%B7%B1%E7%9A%84%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2/</url>
    <content><![CDATA[<p>大佬，我博客的目录结构</p>
<figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">/D/MyBlog/themes/shokaX</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<p>我尝试在 git 中的 MyBlog / 下和 MyBlog/themes/shokaX 下都安装</p>
<figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">npm install --save hexo-algolia</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<p>然后 MyBlog/themes/shokaX/-config.yml 都尝试配置</p>
<figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">algolia:</span><br><span class="line">  appId:  <span class="comment">#我的 appId</span></span><br><span class="line">  apiKey: <span class="comment">#我的 apiKey</span></span><br><span class="line">  adminApiKey: <span class="comment">#我的 adminApiKey</span></span><br><span class="line">  chunkSize: 5000</span><br><span class="line">  indexName: <span class="string">&quot;shokaX&quot;</span></span><br><span class="line">  fields:</span><br><span class="line">    - title</span><br><span class="line">    - path  </span><br><span class="line">    - categories </span><br><span class="line">    - content:strip:<span class="built_in">truncate</span>,0,2000</span><br><span class="line">    - gallery</span><br><span class="line">    - photos</span><br><span class="line">    - tags</span><br><span class="line">   </span><br><span class="line"></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<p>编辑完成后， 执行了 hexo algolia 报错</p>
<figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">Administrator@DESKTOP-1F9O0DC MINGW64 /d/MyBlog</span><br><span class="line">$ hexo algolia</span><br><span class="line">INFO  Validating config</span><br><span class="line">FATAL Something<span class="string">&#x27;s wrong. Maybe you can find the solution here: https://hexo.io/docs/troubleshooting.html</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="string">AlgoliaSearchError: Please provide an application ID. Usage: algoliasearch(applicationID, apiKey, opts)</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="string">    at AlgoliaSearchNodeJS.AlgoliaSearchCore (D:\MyBlog\themes\shokaX\node_modules\hexo-algolia\node_modules\algoliasearch\src\AlgoliaSearchCore.js:50:11)</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="string">    at AlgoliaSearchNodeJS.AlgoliaSearch (D:\MyBlog\themes\shokaX\node_modules\hexo-algolia\node_modules\algoliasearch\src\AlgoliaSearch.js:11:21)</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="string">    at AlgoliaSearchNodeJS.AlgoliaSearchServer (D:\MyBlog\themes\shokaX\node_modules\hexo-algolia\node_modules\algoliasearch\src\server\builds\AlgoliaSearchServer.js:17:17)</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="string">    at new AlgoliaSearchNodeJS (D:\MyBlog\themes\shokaX\node_modules\hexo-algolia\node_modules\algoliasearch\src\server\builds\node.js:83:23)</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="string">    at algoliasearch (D:\MyBlog\themes\shokaX\node_modules\hexo-algolia\node_modules\algoliasearch\src\server\builds\node.js:68:10)</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="string">    at D:\MyBlog\themes\shokaX\node_modules\hexo-algolia\lib\command.js:73:16</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="string"></span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
]]></content>
